## Data note

This repository does not redistribute Stanford SALT Lab's WORKBank dataset.
WORKBank is fetched at build time from
https://huggingface.co/datasets/SALT-NLP/WORKBank
and has no declared upstream license as of 2026-04-24.

Only the derivative tables produced by this pipeline
(`data/capability_2026.csv`, `data/has_drift_2026.csv`, `data/drift_summary.csv`)
and all code in this repository are released under the MIT License above.

Please cite:
  Shao, Zope, Jiang, Pei, Nguyen, Brynjolfsson, Yang.
  "Future of Work with AI Agents: Auditing Automation and Augmentation
  Potential across the U.S. Workforce." arXiv:2506.06576, 2025.
